Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:34.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是要以志願者身份參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:37.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,由於是社區舉辦的活動  預算上稍稍有些吃緊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:40.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是說要出場費
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:44.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是表演也就學藝會這樣的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:47.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,靠這間公寓的人是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:48.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是有劇本的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:51.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣拿著劇本照著讀也行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:53.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:56.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的住客可不好對付
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:58.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,能試著說服他們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:01.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒有好女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:02.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,女性住客居多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:04.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個男性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:08.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此  也僅限於「女人」的範疇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:09.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:14.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,「算是女人嗎  女人嗎」這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:16.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,原先是男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:19.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那華麗麗的不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:22.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,華麗？那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:22.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,非常過分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:25.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在說誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.61,0:02:28.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只要需要我們隨時都能出場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:29.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:33.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會去當眾出醜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是很有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不行了  環姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:38.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:41.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這位女性真是魅力不凡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:46.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這種女性一登上舞台將會多麼華麗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:46.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:47.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:49.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是這位黑衣服的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:51.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:53.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,「這個」是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:56.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,能登台表演嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:01.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個罪孽深重的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,多種意義上來說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:03.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:06.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今年想做成音樂劇的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:07.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:08.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,台詞串成歌詞表現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:13.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌啊  真傷腦筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我會是主角哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這自信從哪來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,以前是兒童合唱團的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:20.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:26.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,再說了丸富公園祭典上有表演會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,銀子  去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:30.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:31.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:34.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:38.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,或許會很愉快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,因為五月雨莊的成員表演哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得會很有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,會去看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那個暗繪小姐要唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:49.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:54.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,堅信著出外爭戰的丈夫一直獨守空閨的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是重點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:56.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:59.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,算了  這次就讓給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:02.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  再稍稍華麗點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.95,0:04:04.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有鮮豔點的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.15,0:04:06.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這身衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.07,0:04:08.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,打算把它當作喪服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這話題就打住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,吶  紫呢  紫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:14.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能太顯眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:16.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就當松樹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這種讓大衛來演就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:24.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你出不出演還要問問紅香小姐再決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  音樂劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:31.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還要唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:34.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡舉行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在丸富公園
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾能有50人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:41.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,加上參加祭典的人  數量不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:43.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,地點怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:46.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,很危險  無法事先預知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:49.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,或許能給紫留下一個美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:50.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  可以參加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:57.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅香小姐  那很危險  要是被找到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎  回憶是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:01.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就是OK了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:09.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,關於那件事…彌生很可能去表演
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候要麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  好的  再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是新工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:17.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:34.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:37.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得混著走調的聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  再來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:45.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,下面按照順序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,由環姐開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好  小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:01.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,暗繪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:14.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道誰走調了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:21.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…暗繪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼奇怪的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:25.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:26.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:29.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還是直說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:30.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,差勁…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:30.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:32.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡有問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,差勁…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小紫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:35.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:36.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}差勁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:40.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有點  真的只有一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:39.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}呐  我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:41.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,換主角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這角色非我莫屬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.12,0:06:45.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都說不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:46.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,差勁…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:47.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:49.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她去說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:54.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…那個…音程有點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.30,0:06:55.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:57.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有點而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的只是一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:04.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這又不是用偶像明星做主角的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這個程度就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:07.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,環姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有誰叫你把我當成偶像明星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:14.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真掃興  我不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:15.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,暗繪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:17.13,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:18.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:19.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊練習一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:20.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,單獨開小灶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就像補習一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:24.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,補習？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,跟不上進度的學生才會有的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別以為我不作聲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,明明有在說話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:32.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別管她了  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:36.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別把我當作跟不上進度的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:37.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,腐爛的蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:38.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:42.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,跟不上進度的學生就叫做腐爛的蜜柑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:44.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:44.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:45.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:46.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}暗繪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:46.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:47.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,酸酸甜甜的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:51.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蜜柑…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在問那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,進行得不是很順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:02.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫唱歌還行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:04.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  唱得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪學過聲樂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:08.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:15.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽唱歌時一直笑容滿面  平靜和藹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:19.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,她教會了我很多歌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:23.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,也想讓媽媽看到小紫登台呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:26.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:29.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別說這個了  我們兩個練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:40.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,以前是兒童合唱團的成員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小學時代我家對面的小純
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對面的  小純
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:47.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:51.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,經常一起玩  她唱歌真好聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:55.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,去合唱團的只是那個女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:56.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:57.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,暗繪小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:02.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為我的少女時代會把時間花費在這上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你騙了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:09.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,最近  小孩犯罪事件增多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:13.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼溫柔的孩子居然是兇犯的案件也比比皆是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.84,0:09:15.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這些有什麼關聯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是時代的錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:22.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別歸結到時代上去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:24.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是政治不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:26.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的總理大臣是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:27.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,美空雲雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:31.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,找別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:32.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,如此突然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:44.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怕老婆的男人打電話時也邊鞠躬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:46.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.57,op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:43.90,op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:45.90,op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:49.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:54.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是需要我這樣的聲音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得還是想不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:58.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼開始練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:15.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  真的糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還是我好一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:19.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:20.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:21.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:29.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這段比較難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得很難唱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:37.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還真是見人說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:40.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,和對我態度真是千差萬別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:43.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我還是能夠勝任的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:44.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,能的  能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:47.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:02.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得和大家格格不入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是這個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.16,0:11:09.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  你覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  真的糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:13.58,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:14.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:17.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼把我們從房間裡攆出來 我不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:21.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,隨他們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:24.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,跟差勁的傢伙一起會被拖後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:29.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,用日語不能溝通還真痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:38.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那個  能跟著我唱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:39.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我會做示範的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:43.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  哪裡是真九郎的部分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.04,0:11:46.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:48.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子真令人吃不消呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:59.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不對  夕乃姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:01.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,害羞可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:02.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:03.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,要再這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:05.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,夕乃姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:05.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快達到高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:08.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:06.77,op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:09.44,op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這一幕就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:11.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,夕乃姐姐  還是抓緊練歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎  不能中途停止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐啊  大衛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.81,0:12:27.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在等男朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:31.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼年輕還是找氣派點賓館吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:32.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要上班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:37.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒在等同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是同伴的話  會先去吃飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:40.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:43.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:47.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你能唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:47.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:51.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在卡拉OK裡最高紀錄95分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:52.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只是卡拉OK的分數
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你試著唱唱看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:58.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,唱一小段就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一小段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:01.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:28.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道稍稍有些問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:29.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:31.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你好閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:32.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,才不閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:33.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:35.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我給你磕頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.66,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:42.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不  請教教我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:52.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,停停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是歌唱力的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:57.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,表情也要柔和點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:01.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我在壞女人當中也屬於酷酷那一類型的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:01.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,笑容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,很早就遺忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,以前和我交往的男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:07.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這話題就打住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:11.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這身服裝也沒有融入角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:13.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會脫下這套衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:14.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎樣也不？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:16.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,想把它當作喪服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:17.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這身衣服啊  以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是記者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:24.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:27.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我教你如何使用壓倒性的技術迷倒觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道衣服的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:34.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎這傢伙  還發誓會保護紫的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:36.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,男人的愛情是另存為
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,女人的愛情是覆蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:39.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,男人能腳踏很多船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,新歡舊愛都能兼顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:49.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,女人要是找到新的男人就把過去的男人忘得一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也到環的房間裡睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:54.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,故事沒變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:03.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都這樣了 乾脆換個故事比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:06.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我也認為村姑A沒法發揮我的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我們也換換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:09.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:12.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小紫演女主角的幼年時代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這主意不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:20.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  這樣下去溝通都成問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起合唱的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:25.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,任何困難都能度過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對了  一起的話就能度過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:30.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  夕乃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我二重唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:33.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,二重唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是二重唱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:36.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:50.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:56.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.67,0:19:02.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今夜的歌聲真令人愉悅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:05.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:07.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:08.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:13.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮弗  你這個不可饒恕的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪格瑞特  你這個下賤的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,朝陽真耀眼  瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:19.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}咦 不是結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:22.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭  你酒喝多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}剛才應該是結尾曲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:24.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,說起昨晚的伯爵…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不能算在裡面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:30.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說  我也厭倦與瑪格瑞特在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:33.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這算是戀愛的煩惱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:37.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕人只想著戀愛啊愛情什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:39.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}卻對政治毫無興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪格瑞特究竟是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:44.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}總之  我們也算是趣味相投了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有珍妮弗這個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:47.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,惠和新一  這舞台明明在日本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:51.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮弗  珍妮弗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.71,0:19:57.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了  約會地點應該是這沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮弗  別嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.79,0:20:02.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}日本人出場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:04.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那個女人是外國人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:07.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天會讓你更加大吃一驚的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿珍妮弗沒轍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:09.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}有點不合拍的感覺倒是有點像外國人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:11.38,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:12.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是受叔叔的影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.59,0:20:15.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  別把我們相提並論啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:18.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:22.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,說讓我大吃一驚  難道是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:25.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  這話要讓我說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:26.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:27.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔  噓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:30.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.73,0:20:38.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  很難得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}（God  mother）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:40.37,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:43.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是活生生的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:46.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:02.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不能靠近這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:06.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,柔澤紅香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:10.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,完全聯絡不上真九郎和我的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:12.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,又是你做的好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:13.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:19.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:23.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在丸富公園辦音樂劇是假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,今年應該是漫才才對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:30.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是裝蒜的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:34.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:38.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,平時都沒時間玩樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:41.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我想創造個機會而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:44.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  那個委員會成員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是我雇的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:46.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,表演會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:48.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:52.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道為了這麼無聊的事我受了多少羞辱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.63,0:21:54.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:59.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,克服困難的結果是和真九郎度過了如此親密無間的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:01.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,紫也很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.06,0:22:06.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你們認為事情這麼容易了結嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.23,0:22:12.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,傑姆斯選中的女人被判刑而死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:16.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪格瑞特和珍妮弗的命運還是未知數呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:16.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.09,0:22:19.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,最後一幕還沒完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:19.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:21.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,都站起身來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.11,0:22:22.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,給我爬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:23.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,到珍妮弗的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:25.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,奔向瑪格瑞特的懷抱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.61,0:22:26.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  齊聲歌唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:28.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為嶄新的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:30.58,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為嶄新的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:31.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.69,0:22:34.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我好睏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:39.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}（你的頭頂閃爍著光芒吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:20.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,下集  紅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.08,0:24:22.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:26.01,op,,0000,0000,0000,,翼しんじ　大空まで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:34.73,op,,0000,0000,0000,,君も飛ぶよ　僕も行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:54.90,op,,0000,0000,0000,,果ての果て　飛んでゆける
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:06:01.62,op,,0000,0000,0000,,翼しんじ　大空まで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:12.10,op,,0000,0000,0000,,君も飛ぶよ　僕も行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:36.39,op,,0000,0000,0000,,君も飛ぶよ　僕も行く…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:09.83,op,,0000,0000,0000,,君も飛ぶよ　僕も行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:58.49,op,,0000,0000,0000,,君も飛ぶよ　僕も行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:34.26,op,,0000,0000,0000,,僕も行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:57.69,op,,0000,0000,0000,,すぐに飛ぶよ　大空まで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.69,op,,0000,0000,0000,,それでもいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.86,0:13:11.01,op,,0000,0000,0000,,許されないこいだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:16.23,op,,0000,0000,0000,,あなたがくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:21.10,op,,0000,0000,0000,,指輪が冷たい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:51.40,op,,0000,0000,0000,,捨てなくではいけないこともあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:19.97,op,,0000,0000,0000,,光になれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.30,op,,0000,0000,0000,,翼しんじ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.38,op,,0000,0000,0000,,翼しんじ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.89,op,,0000,0000,0000,,大空まで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:50.63,op,,0000,0000,0000,,大空まで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.58,0:15:55.67,op,,0000,0000,0000,,君も飛ぶよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:16:02.10,op,,0000,0000,0000,,僕も行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:08.19,op,,0000,0000,0000,,二人で飛ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:14.56,op,,0000,0000,0000,,光になれ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:25.53,op,,0000,0000,0000,,真九郎さん敵が攻めてきたわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:28.43,op,,0000,0000,0000,,あいつは敵だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:34.30,op,,0000,0000,0000,,騙されじゃだめよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:41.98,op,,0000,0000,0000,,ジェニファは汚れた女だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:49.66,op,,0000,0000,0000,,少しは話を聞いて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:55.98,op,,0000,0000,0000,,少しでいいの　立ちながらでも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:17:10.91,op,,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの声でも　救われるの明日を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:17.50,op,,0000,0000,0000,,声が響く　こだまするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:23.01,op,,0000,0000,0000,,邪悪な声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:29.79,op,,0000,0000,0000,,返してくれ　返してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:35.37,op,,0000,0000,0000,,奪えよマリア
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:41.88,op,,0000,0000,0000,,私の場所　私の役
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:47.53,op,,0000,0000,0000,,あなたの役
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:18:00.09,op,,0000,0000,0000,,乱れた人　壊さないで　あいつは嫌
